: P I D E R R (Prepare, Identify, Contain, Eradicate, Recover, Review)

Steps:

Preparation: IR plan, tools, training, logging, backups.

Identification: Confirm alerts, scope, impacted systems.

Containment: Isolate affected systems, block IPs, prevent spread.

Eradication: Remove malware, patch vulnerabilities, reset credentials, reimage if needed.

Recovery: Restore from clean backups, monitor systems.

Lessons Learned: Post-incident review, update IR plan, train users
